<h2>Northern Lights Adventure holidays</h2>
<p><strong>Some people choose to visit Lapland for the skiing, the winter activities such as husky or reindeer rides but a lot of people book a holiday to Lapland to chase the Northern Lights.</strong> </p>
<p>Therefore, we offer you a choice of <strong>two types of Northern Lights adventure themed holidays</strong> with fantastic additional extras available for you to add on to any holiday.</p>
<p>Our <strong>Northern Lights Adventure Weeks</strong> are based at the Muotka Wilderness Lodge, located near Saariselkä. You can stay in the lodge for an entire week, or spend 3 nights here combined with 4 nights in Saariselkä.</p>
<p>Our holidays to the the <strong>Muotka Wilderness Lodge</strong> include many Northern Lights activities, maximising your chances of the seeing the Aurora for yourself.</p>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Muotka 7 Night Adventure</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/fd2e5d7929b4463883ca4109fd714cc4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fd2e5d7929b4463883ca4109fd714cc4}" title="Muotka 7 Night Adventure"><img src="/media/13082791/ht4a4927.jpg" alt="Muotka 7 night adventure" data-udi="umb://media/83ba67bde2bd48efbbfe1514fdaa10c2" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Spend 7 nights, which is the duration of your stay, in <a data-udi="umb://document/5fff74e4dcc94dfab5862d08d14d26c2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5fff74e4dcc94dfab5862d08d14d26c2}" title="Muotka Wilderness Lodge">Wilderness Hotel Muotka</a></p>
