<h2 style="text-align: center;">Muotka 2-Centre Adventure</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7d16724b0f3b4033952b780a65425621" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d16724b0f3b4033952b780a65425621}" title="Muotka 2-Centre Adventure"><img src="/media/13082792/muotka-wilderness-lodge-kota.jpg" alt="Muotka 2 centre adventure" data-udi="umb://media/dd93153106dd466e9624c2b3a8de1406" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Spend 4 nights in either <a data-udi="umb://document/3d7dc001611746319bcefb1b23f134d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3d7dc001611746319bcefb1b23f134d1}" title="Gielas Hotel">Gielas Hotel</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/c661c78119c84b88b761eef9614441f2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c661c78119c84b88b761eef9614441f2}" title="Holiday Club Spa Hotel">Holiday Club Hotel</a> &amp; 3 nights in <a data-udi="umb://document/5fff74e4dcc94dfab5862d08d14d26c2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5fff74e4dcc94dfab5862d08d14d26c2}" title="Muotka Wilderness Lodge">Wilderness Hotel Muotka</a>.<a data-udi="umb://document/7d16724b0f3b4033952b780a65425621" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d16724b0f3b4033952b780a65425621}?0 style=" title="Muotka 2-Centre Adventure" data-anchor="?0 style="></a></p>
