<h2 style="text-align: left;">Lapland Excursions</h2>
<br />Though you may visit Lapland for the Aurora Borealis, there is so much more to see and experience. Have a look at some of the fantastic Excursions and Safaris that you can enjoy during your time in Lapland, including additional ways to see the Northern Lights:</div>
<div class="g12"><br />
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Glass Igloo &amp; Aurora Cabin Excursion</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7a950f997b0d4f868205f0e6f8e60cdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7a950f997b0d4f868205f0e6f8e60cdf}" title="Glass Igloo &amp; Aurora Cabin Excursion"><img src="/media/13073432/muotka-aurora-cabin-3.jpg?width=838&amp;height=450&amp;mode=max" alt="Muotka Aurora Cabin" width="838" height="450" data-udi="umb://media/d544b74372ff436d9a6a187d06671132" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span>A <a data-udi="umb://document/9933a896cd594899ac7150e009590145" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9933a896cd594899ac7150e009590145}" title="Northern Lights Adventures">glass igloo and aurora cabin excursion</a> is a <em>must have</em> experience on your <a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Lapland</a> holiday.</span></p>
