<p style="text-align: left;"><span>Chase the Northern lights in more than one way with night-time <a data-udi="umb://document/e9d443cb665d4899b74aa61005c34869" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e9d443cb665d4899b74aa61005c34869}" title="Ice Activities">Snowshoeing</a> to evening <a data-udi="umb://document/345a78d93ecb4821a7eb5c47c0382ee6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/345a78d93ecb4821a7eb5c47c0382ee6}" title="Snowmobile Safari">snowmobile safaris</a>. </span><a data-udi="umb://document/7d16724b0f3b4033952b780a65425621" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d16724b0f3b4033952b780a65425621}?0 style=" title="Muotka 2-Centre Adventure" data-anchor="?0 style="></a></p>
