<h2 align="center" style="text-align: left;">Northern Lights Insiders Guides</h2>
<p>Know all you need to know before you embark on an adventure of a life-time with the help of our Insider's Guides.</p>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="color: #023761;"><strong>Insider’s Guide: </strong></h3>
<p style="color: #023761;"><strong>Where to see the Northern Lights this winter</strong></p>
<p><img src="/media/13079889/southern-lakes-resort-northern-lights.jpeg" alt="wheretosee" data-udi="umb://media/526206d4b4f743618d905636996992b3" /></p>
<p>The Aurora Borealis, better known as the Northern Lights, regularly tops bucket lists as one experience to enjoy during your lifetime. Seek out this magical sight with Inghams.</p>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button" style="height: 49px; width: 273px; background-color: #ffffff; border-color: #f26419; float: left;">
