</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="color: #023761;"><strong>Insider’s Guide: </strong></h3>
<p style="color: #023761;"><strong>How to photograph the Northern Lights</strong></p>
<p><img src="/media/13084141/northern-lights-colours.jpg" alt="photolights" data-udi="umb://media/6c7176e081ef47b28fa520db54f9db53" /></p>
<p>Witnessing the Northern Lights is an unforgettable experience, one you’ll treasure for a lifetime. Master the essential skills to get the perfect photograph to remember it by.</p>
